  1. Kian7-choan5 e5 Cheng-sin5 tiam3 ti7 Kian7-choan5 e5 Seng-khu 
  ¡§Kian7-choan5 e5 Cheng-sin5 tiam3 ti7 Kian7-choan5 e5 Seng-khu¡¨ (Mens sana in corpore sano). Chit ku3 si7 Se-iuN5 e5 kek-gian5, si7 bian2-le7 lang5 tioh8 gau5 hun3-lian7 chiau3-kou3 seng-khu hou7 i iong2 e5 chhut-mia5 e5 oe7. Se-iuN5 e5 lang5 ko3-ko3 to si7 kah-na2 chhin-chhiuN7 chiong chit ku3-oe7 khek ti7 in e5 nau2-kin-lai7, in tak8 lang5 put-lun7 ta-pou, cha-bou2, toa7-lang5 gin2-na2, long2 si7 hui-siong5 gau5 hun3-lian7 seng-khu. Sou2-i2 in e5 lang5 m7-na7 seng-khu e5 kin-bah si7 chhin-chhiuN7 thih phah--e5, in e5 cheng-sin5 ko3-ko3 to si7 oah8-thiau3-thiau3. 
  Lan2 e5 lang5 m7-chai si7 ui7-tioh8 sim2-mih8 ian5-kou3, kok-lang5 e5 seng-khu to si7 be7-hiau2-tit chiau3-kou3--e5 khah-che7, ti3-kau3 the2-chit hui-siong5 lam2, cheng-sin5 long2 bo5 kau3-giah8. Phou2-thong na7 chiah8 kau3 gou7-chap8 hoe3 , chiu7 giam2-jian5 u7 chit8 e5 lau7-lang5 khoan2. Se-iuN5 lang5 tui3 gou7-chap8 hoe3 khi2, tu2-chiah si7 beh toa7-toa7 cho3 tai7-chi3; in hit-tiap8 e5 cheng-sin5 chha-put-to si7 kap lan2 ji7-saN-chap8 hoe3 e5 lang5 tang5 chit8-iuN7, kui seng-khu moa2-moa2 to si7 chong3-lian5 e5 khi3-khai3. 
  U7 lang5 kong2 Tang-iuN5 kap Se-iuN5 e5 bun5-beng5 kok-kok u7 tek8-sek, bo5 tek-khak Se-iuN5 u7 khah-iaN5. Goa2 siuN7 liong2-peng5 e5 bun5-beng5 kok u7 tek8-sek, che khiok si7 sit8-chai7; chong2-si7 kong2 Tang-iuN5 e5 bun5-beng5 be7 khah-su Se-iuN5, che kiaN cho3 kong2-liau2 siuN chu7-khoa. Koh-khah an2-choaN2 siuN7 , goa2 to m7-kaN2 kong2 Tang-iuN5 e5 bun5-beng5 be7 khah-su. Lang5 kong2, Tang-iuN5 e5 bun5-beng5 si7 chai7 ti7 cheng-sin5; Se-iuN5 si7 chai7 but8-chit. An2-ni si7 u7-iaN2 ; chong2-si7 m7-thang tui3 an2-ni chiu7 liah8-cho3 Se-iuN5 e5 cheng-sin5 bo5 bun5-beng5, a2-si7 kong2 Se-iuN5 e5 cheng-sin5 bun5-beng5 si7 khah-su Tang-iuN5--e5. Na7-si7 chit8-tiam2 tu2 chit8-tiam2 lai5 pheng7, Tang-iuN5 e5 cheng-sin5 bun5-beng5 , lai7-te2 pi2 Se-iuN5--e5 khah chhut-sek ia7 si7 u7; m7-ku2 na7 tui3 tai7-the2 khoaN3, thang kong2 m7-na7 Se-iuN5 e5 but8-chit bun5-beng5 u7 khah-iaN5 Tang-iuN5, cheng-sin5 bun5-beng5 iah8 si7 pi2 lan2 khah chhut-tioh. 
  Chong2-kong2 , Se-iuN5 bun5-beng5 si7 khah chek-kek8, lan2 Tang-iuN5 bun5-beng5 si7 khah siau-kek8. Se-iuN5--e5 si7 khah hiong3-chian5 khah oah8-tang7; lan2--e5 , si7 khah siu2, khah tim5-cheng7, khah the3-pi7, khah iu-ut e5 khoan2. Phi3-lun7 kong2: Chai7 lan2 si7 kong2, ¡§Ka-ti7 sou2 m7-ai3--e5 m7-thang hou7 pat8-lang5, an2-ni chiu7-si7 u7 jin5-ai3.¡¨ Chai7 Se-iuN5 chiu7 m7-si7 an2-ni. In kong2, ¡§Tioh8 chiong ka-ti7 sou2 ai3--e5, hoaN-hi2 hou7 lang5, chiah si7 u7 jin5-ai3.¡¨
  Kin7-kin7 tui3 chit ku3-oe7 chiu7 e7 thang chai-iaN2 Se-iuN5 e5 cheng-sin5 khah chek-kek8, khah thiat-te2. ChhiaN2 jin7-chin siuN7-khoaN3 leh, lan2 sou2 m7-ai3--e5 boh8-tit theh8 hou7 lang5 si7 khah-khoai3, chiong lan2 sou2 ai3--e5 theh8 hou7 lang5, sit8-chai7 si7 khah-oh. Koh-chai3 chiong lan2 sou2 m7-ai3--e5 bo5 theh8 hou7 lang5; tui3 hit e5 lang5 kong2 si7 bo5 ui7-tioh8 an2-ni ke-thiN sim2-mih8 hoe3, si7 peng5-siong5 e5 tai7-chi3. M7-ku2 na7 chiau3 lan2 sou2 ai3-e5 theh8 hou7 i, hit e5 lang5 ui7-tioh8 an2-ni ke-thiN li7-ek si7 khah che7. 
  Se-iuN5 e5 chong-kau3 (Ki-tok-kau3 ) ka3 lang5 kong2, Lang5 e5 seng-khu si7 seng3-leng5 e5 po2-tian2, sou2-i2 tui3 seng-khu lai7 sou2 hoat-chhut it-chhe3 e5 kam2-kak, na7 siu7 seng3-leng5 e5 chi2-to7 , tioh8 long2 hou7 i oah8-tang7 chiah ho2. Tang-iuN5 e5 chong-kau3( Put8-kau3) ka3 lang5 kong2, se3-kan ban7-su7 si7 khang-khang. Chiu7-si7 lang5 seng-khu kiat-kiok8 ia7 si7 bo5; na7 chiong bo5-e5 khoaN3 cho3 u7, chiu7-si7 chip-be5, sou2-i2 tui3 seng-khu sou2 hoat it-chhe3 e5 kam2-kak, tioh8 ka7 i kim3-che3 hou7 i siau-bo5--khi3. Tui3 an2-ni sin3 Put8-kau3 e5 lang5 u7-e5 bo5 chhoa7 bou2, u7-e5 kim3 bo5 khun3, bo5 chiah8-png7, kong2 iah8 u7 kau2-ni5 ku2 kan-ta tiam7-tiam7 che7 khoaN3-piah, ia7 u7-e5 che7 teng-chhng5, kiah8 chng3-a2 chhak8 seng-khu, hou7 pat8 khoan2 e5 liam7-thau5 be7 hoat-seN, hou7 jiok8-the2 e7 thang khah kin2 bo5--khi3, thang seng5 Put8. Liat8-ui7 , chhiaN2 siuN7-khoaN3, chit nng7 khoan2 chong-kau3, si7 Tang Sai nng7-peng5 cheng-sin5 bun5-beng5 e5 toa7 tek8-sek. Chiau3 an2-ni pi2-kau3 khoaN3, Tang-iuN5 Put8-kau3 sou2 kong2 kiam2 m7-si7 hui-siong5 siau-kek8 mah? 
  Koh-chai3 Se-iuN5 lang5 tui3 thiN-te7-kan ban7-hang7-mih8 long2 si7 bo5 kiaN-hiaN5 ; in long2 kaN2 oa2-kin7 ka7 i gian2-kiu3 kau3 chin, ka7 i theh8-lai5 cho3 lang5 e5 lou7-eng7. Lan2 Tang-iuN5 lang5 chiu7 m7-kaN2; tai7-khai3 e5 mih8 to si7 m7-kaN2 khi3 bong--i. Phi2-lun7 kong2, lan2 Tang-iuN5 lang5 kiah8-hiuN teh pai3 e5 lui5-kong sih-na3; Se-iuN5 lang5 in long2 bo5 kap i se3-ji7, ka7 i chhoa7--lai5, chiu7 kio3 i cho3 gu5 thoa-chhia, cho3 teng chio3-lou7. In Se-iuN5 lang5 chai7 chit te7-bin7-chiuN7 bo5 chit8 tah in m7-kaN2 kau3; lan2 e5 lang5 si7 kan-ta cheng2-kah lau5 tng5-tng5, tiam3 chhu3-lai7 kiaN5-lai5 kiaN5-khi3, siau3 chng-a2 thit-tho5 koe3-jit8. 
  Lun7 kin-a2-jit8 e5 Tang-iuN5 lang5 su Se-iuN5 lang5 e5 tiam2 si7 chin-che7 lah. Lan2 Tang-iuN5 lang5 e5 chi3-khi3 si7 chin siau-tim5, chin bo5 oah8-tang7. Lan2 long2 chin khoai3 lau7, chin khoai3 si2. Che long2 si7 tui3 lan2 e5 sin-the2 chin loan2-jiok8, ti3-kau3 cheng-sin5 bo5 chhiong-chiok. Sou2-i2 su7-su7 to si7 m7-kaN2 hiong3-cheng5 cho3, long2 si7 the3-pou7 siu2 na7-tiaN7. ¡§Kian7-choan5 e5 cheng-sin5 si7 tiam3 ti7 kian7-choan5 e5 seng-khu.¡¨
  Liat8-ui7 , chhiaN2 lan2 e5 bak8-chiu thi2-khui khoaN3 , lan2 e5 lang5 u7 chiaN5 chit8 e5 lang5-khoan2--e5, u7 kui2 lang5? Khah-che7 kiam2 m7-si7 bin7-sek kou-ta5, phoe5-bah siau-san2, un2-ku, chhiN-me5, pai2-kha--e5 moa2-moa2 si7 mah? Tui3 chit khoan2 the2-keh bo5 kiong5-chong7 e5 cheng-sin5 thang hoat-hian7, sit8-chai7 si7 eng-kai. 
  2. E7 thang hou7 seng-khu iong2-kiaN7 e5 hoat-tou7 
  Lan2 beh gian2-kiu3 hou7 seng-khu e7 thang kiong5-chong3 e5 hoat-tou7 e5 i2-cheng5, lan2 tioh8 seng e7 ki3-tit chit8 hang7: chiu7-si7 lan2 ai3 seng-khu iong2, m7-si7 beh ai3 tng5 hoe3-siu7 e5 i3-su3, si7 beh ai3 lan2 chin7 cho3 lang5 e5 pun2-hun7, cho3 hou7 i thiat-te2. Na7 m7-si7 an2-ni siuN7, kong2 hou7 seng-khu iong2, si7 choan-choan ui7-tioh8 beh ai3 tng5-hoe3-siu7 e5 ian5-kou3, an2-ni chiu7 toa7-toa7 u7 chho3-gou7, koh loh8-khi3 sou2 beh kong2 e5 gi7-lun7 chiu7 soa3 be7 beng5-pek8. 
  ChhiaN2 siuN7-khoaN3 , chia u7 chit8 ki to. To, m7-si7 beh pai5 khoaN3-hong2. To, si7 beh chhiat mih8. To, na7 e7 thang chhiat ju2-che7 khoan2, koh ju2-che7 e5 mih8, si7 ju2 ho2. To, kan-ta sok ti7 to-siu3, sui-jian5 si7 khng3 u7 kui2-na7 chheng ni5 e5 ku2, kiat-kiok8 u7 sim2-mih8 i3-gi7? To, tioh8 chhiat mih8, chhiat ju2-che7 ju2-ho2 . Sou2-i2 to, te7-it iau3-kin2 tioh8 u7 kng3; te7-ji7 , tioh8 ai3 lai7. To , beh ai3 u7 kng3 tioh8 ai3 eng7 hoe2 pu5, eng7 thui5 lian7, eng7 chui2 gan3, iah8 beh hou7 i lai7 chiu7 tioh8 siah, tioh8 boa5. Na7-si7 an2-ni, hit ki to tiaN7-tioh8 e7 khah khoai3 liau2; iah8 kiaN khoai3 liau2, chiong to bo5 siah bo5 boa5, kan-ta siu khi3 khng3, kiu3-keng3 si7 chiaN5-sim2-mih8? Chit e5 i3-gi7 na7 u7 beng5, beh hou7 seng-khu e7 iong2-chong3 e5 hoat-tou7 chiu7 khah khoai3 chheng-chho2. 
  A. Hioh-khun3 kap cho3-kang 
  Hioh-khun3 kap cho3-kang, chun2-chat hou7 tu2-ho2, beh hou7 seng-khu iong2, chit hang7 si7 choe3 iau3-kin2. Lan2 peng5-siong5 e5 lang5 put-chi2 khin5-bian2, long2 si7 e7-hiau2 siuN7 cho3-kang, be7-hiau2 siuN7 hiok-khun3. Se-iuN5 u7 chit8 ku3 siok8-gu2 kong2, ¡§Bo5 hioh-khun3 long2 cho3-kang, khiau2-khiau2 gin2-na2 to e7 piN3 gong7-lang5.¡¨ Lan2 it-poaN e5 lang5 chiau3-khoaN3 khah-che7 si7 cho3-kang koe3-thau5, siau-san2 tit8-tit8 beh ta-khi3--e5 si7 chin-che7. Iah8 chit8 peng5 u7 giap8-san2 u7 te7-ui7 e5 lang5, put-chi2 m7-ai3 tin2-tang7, choan-choan si7 hioh-khun3. In e5 hioh-khun3 thang kong2 si7 chin kek8-toan e5 cho3-hoat, i e5 kha-chhiu2 chha-put-to kui-si3-lang5 long2 m7-bat hou7 i tin2-tang7; i e5 mng5-kng2-khang, tu5-khi3 phoa3-peN7 hoat-jiat8 a2-si7 lak8-goeh8 thiN i2-goa7, thang kong2 si7 long2 m7-bat u7 lau5-koaN7 chhut-lai5. Sou2-i2 khah-che7 si7 kap peng5-siong5 lang5 siang7-khoan2, iu5-goan5 si7 chit8 teng5-phoe5 ne5 chit8 ki kut, nng7 ki kha chai3 chit8 e5 seng-khu to soa3 beh be7 chai7. Lan2 e5 lang5 thang kong2 si7 kek8-toan kau3-kek8 , cho3-kang--e5 tit8-tit8 cho3 kau3 si2, iah8 hioh-khun3--e5 bi7 it-tit8 khun3 kau3 khui3-si tng7. Che si7 i e5 keng2-gu7 kio3 i an2-ni iah8 si7 u7; chong2-si7 toa7 e5 li2-iu5 si7 be7-hiau2 cho3-kang kap hioh-khun3 e5 i3-gi7.
  Tang7 kha-chhiu2, be7 iong7-tit kong2 si7 teh cho3-kang; tiam7-tiam7 che7, iah8 be7 iong7-tit kong2 si7 teh hioh-khun3. Cho3-kang kap hioh-khun3 e5 hun-piat8, khoaN3 si7 ui7-tioh8 tai7-chi3 teh cho3 tai7-chi3, a2-si7 ui7-tioh8 sim-ai3 teh cho3 tai7-chi3. Ui7-tioh8 tai7-chi3 teh cho3 tai7-chi3 si7 chhut ti7 bo5-ta5-oa5, si7 u7 kam2-kak kan-khou2. Ui7-tioh8 sim ai3 cho3 tai7-chi3, si7 chhut ti7 sim-koaN ka-ti7 boeh, sou2-i2 u7 an-ui3. Theh8 iu5-pian7 e5 lang5 teh chau2-lou7, chau2 sio-liah8 e5 lang5 iah8 si7 teh chau2-lou7; sui-jian5 si7 peN5-peN5 teh chau2-lou7, theh8 iu5-pian7--e5 si7 teh cho3-kang, chau2 sio-liah8 e5 lang5 si7 teh hioh-khun3. Seng-li2 lang5 ui7-tioh8 seng-li2 phong2 chhui3-e7-tau2 ti7-teh-siuN7, kap kiaN5-ki5 e5 lang5 ui7-tioh8 ki5-ji2 lian2 chhui3-chhiu ti7-teh siuN7, peN5-peN5 to si7 ti7-teh siuN7; chong2-si7 chit8-e5 si7 teh cho3-kang, chit8-e5 si7 teh hioh-khun3. Cho3-kang si7 bo5-ta5-oa5, si7 bian2-kiong2 cho3, si7 ui5-poe7 sim-koaN e5 sou2 ai3, sou2-i2 toa7-toa7 u7 sun2-hai7 seng-khu e5 khong-kian7. Hioh-khun3 si7 chhut ti7 sim sou2 ai3, u7 an-ui3, sou2-i2 tui3 seng-khu e5 kian7-khong u7 li7-ek. Cho3-kang si7 siu7 tai7-chi3 sou2 pek ti7-teh cho3, tai7-chi3 na7 boe7-liau2, kang chiu7 be7 thang soah. 
  Sou2-i2 lo5-tong7 siuN koe3-thau5 , ti3-kau3 hai7 seng-khu. Hioh-khun3 si7 chhut-chai7 sim chu3-i3, ai3 cho3 chiu7 lai5 cho3, ai3 hioh chiu7 e7 thang hioh, chun2-chat e7 tu2-ho2; sou2-i2 tui3 seng-khu u7 li7-ek. Koh-chai3 cho3-kang si7 khah ai3 choan-chu2 ti7 chit8 hang7, siuN7 tai7-chi3--e5 tioh8 put-si5 choan-choan ti7-teh siuN7, chhut-lat8--e5, chhut-kau3 lat8 chin7, to tioh8 ai3 koh chhut, iong7 chhiu2--e5 tioh8 put-si5 iong7 chhiu2, iong7 kha--e5 put-si5 tioh8 iong7 kha, ti7 goa7-bin7--e5 tioh8 hou7 jit8-thau5 phak8 kau3 beh ta--khi3, ti7 lai7-bin7--e5 tioh8 im3 kau3 beh ng5-sng. 
  Chong2-kong2 cho3-kang si7 iong7 seng-khu e5 chit8-pou7, ti3-kau3 choan5-the2 be7 tiau5-ho5, piN3-chiaN5 chit cheng2 phoa3-siuN3 e5 khoan2-sit. Hioh-khun3 e7 thang chiau3 lan2 seng-khu e5 khoat-khiam3, tiau-ho5 hou7 ho2-se3, sou2-i2 seng-khu e7 khong-kian7 , e7 na2 cheng-ka. 
  Lan2 ti7-chia kong2 hioh-khun3 , bian2 kong2 m7-si7 kan-ta to2 teh khun3 e5 i3-su3. Chong2-kong2, chhut ti7 sim-koaN e5 sou2 ai3 lai5 cho3 chiu7-si7 hioh-khun3. Seng-khu ia3-sian7, sim-koaN siuN7 ai3 khun3, iah8 chiu7 to2--loh8-khi3 khun3, an2-ni chiu7-si7 hioh-khun3; che si7 an-cheng7 e5 hioh-khun3. Seng-khu ia3-sian7 , sim-koaN siuN7 ai3 tin2-tang7 , iah8 chiu7 chhut-khi3 goa7-bin7 kiaN5-chau2 , a2-si7 phah-kiu5, peh-soaN, che si7 kio3-cho3 un7-tong7 e5 hioh-khun3. Phou2-thong , lan2 e5 lang5 na7 kong2 hioh-khun3, chiu7-si7 chi2 an-cheng7 e5 i3-su3, long2 bo5 un7-tong7 e5 i3-su3 ti7 hit nih. 
  Chit ku3 un7-tong7 e5 oe7 si7 kin7-lai5 chiah khah u7 eng7, khah-cha2 long2 han2-tit thiaN-kiN3. Che si7 cheng3-beng5 lan2 tui3 un7-tong7 bo5 chhu3-bi7, bo5 koan-sim. Chiong5-lai5 khoaN3 un7-tong7 si7 cho3 chit8 cheng3 m7 cheng3-keng e5 tai7-chi3, gin2-na2 cho3 ng kok8-ke bih sio-chhoe7, a2-si7 tioh koe3-hun5, chhat8 ui5-kun , che-to long2 si7 chit8 cheng2 e5 un7-tong7. It-poaN e5 lang5 khoaN3 che kong2 si7 gin2-na2 teh sng2 teh chok-giat8, liah8-cho3 m7 eng-kai e5 tai7-chi3; toa7-lang5 choat8-tui3 m7-bat cho3, ia7 m7-kheng2 hou7 gin2-na2 khi3 cho3. 
  Kau3 chia, lan2 i2-keng e7 thang beng5-pek8 lan2 e5 lang5 sin-the2 loan2-jiok8 e5 li2-iu5. Lan2 e5 lang5 thang kong2 si7 u7 lo5-tong7, bo5 un7-tong7. Lo5-tong7 , chiau3 teng2-bin7 sou2 kong2 u7 hai7 seng-khu si7 khah-che7; beh hou7 seng-khu iong2, ai3 un7-tong7 chiah e7 iong7-tit. Sui-jian5 kong2 lan2 m7-si7 bo5 hioh-khun3, lan2 si7 kan-ta u7 an-cheng7 e5 hioh-khun3 na7-tiaN7. An-cheng7 , khiok si7 iau3-kin2; chong2-si7 na7 kan-ta an-cheng7, si7 hou7 lang5 e5 kin-bah ju2 bo5 khui3-lat8, hou7 lang5 e5 cheng-sin5 ju2 siau-tim5, ju2 nng2-chiaN2. 
  Tai7-ke cheng3 hiaN-ti7 chi2-moe7! Lan2 siu7 chin ku2 phaiN2 sip8-koan3 e5 chek-pe3 chin chhim, hou7 lan2 seng-khu loan2-jiok8 , i2-keng kau3 kek8-kham2, lan2 e5 cheng-sin5 siau-tim5 i2-keng kau3 ti7 kek8-thau5. Cho3 lang5 eng-kai siu7-tioh8 e5 hok-khi3, lan2 sit8-chai7 pang3-sak chin-chiaN3 che7, chha-put-to bo5 tang3 thang sng3-khi2. Che long2 si7 tui3 lan2 be7-hiau2 cho3-kang kap hioh-khun3 e5 i3-gi7. be7-hiau2 un7-tong7 e5 iau3-kin2 sou2 ti3--e5 . Lan2 tioh8 chhiat-chhiat kin2-kin2 seng2-gou7, kan-ta cho3-kang bo5 hioh-khun3 , kau3-boe2 si7 e7 bo5 kang cho3. Iah8 koh-chai3 na7-si7 kan-ta an-cheng7 bo5 un7-tong7, kau3-boe2 tioh8 ai3 piN3-chiaN5 nng2-kha nng2-chhiu2 e5 sian7-lang5-a2! 
  M7-ai3 un7-tong7, si7 Tang-iuN5 lang5 kiong7-thong e5 seng3-chit. Chit chap8-goa7 ni5 i2-lai5, siu7 Se-iuN5 e5 hong-khi3 toa7 kam2-hoa3, un7-tong7 e5 chhu3-bi7 i2-keng chit8-ni5 chit8-ni5 tiong2. Chai7 hak8-hau7 tak8-jit8 to u7 ka3 un7-tong7 e5 hoat-tou7, mui2-ni5 u7 siat chiong2-chiong2 e5 un7-tong7-hoe7 teh kou2-bu2. M7-na7 tak8 kok tiam3 ti7 i e5 kok-lai7 ka-ti7 teh chiong2-le7; kok tu2 kok e5 tiong-kan ia7 u7 siat-hoe7 teh kou2-chhui. 
  Chai7 lan2 Tang-iuN5, Jit8-pun2 , Tiong-kok, Hui-li7-pin chit saN kok chu7 si3, gou7 ni5 cheng5 u7 siat chit8 e5 hoe7, kio3-cho3 ¡§Kek8-tang Ou-lin5-phi-kuh.¡¨ Nng7 ni5 chiau3-lun5 ti7 chit8 kok khui chit8 pai2. Thong se3-kai3 ban7-kok ia7 u7 sio-kap siat chit8 e5 Se3-kai3 Ou-lin5-phi-kuh e5 hoe7, kaN2-si7 mui2 si3-ni5 khui chit8 pai2. Kin-ni5 (1924) si7 tiam3 Hoat-kok e5 Te3-tou Pa-le5 khui, chit pai2 sng3-si7 te7-peh pai2. Ti7 teng2-goeh8 (4 goeh8 27 jit8) tui3 lan2 kok-lai7 ia7 u7 keng2 ji7-chap8-goa7 lang5 phai3 khi3 hu3 hit e5 hoe7, tioh8 che7 gou7-chap8 jit8 e5 chun5 chiah e7 kau3-ui7. Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni , chit khoan2 e5 hoe7, sou2 khai e5 chiN5 kap sou2 iong7 e5 sim-sin5, sit8-chai7 si7 m7-si7 sio2-khoa2. U7-tang-si5 m7 tu2-ho2 ti7 hit tiong-kan u7 lang5 tioh8-siong, u7 lang5 liau2 seN3-mia7--e5 ia7 si7 bo5 hi-han2. 
  Lau2-sit8, chit khoan2 e5 tai7-chi3 hou7 lan2 e5 lang5 tek-khak si7 cho3 be7-tit-thang kau3; chong2-si7 ui7-tioh8 an2-ni , kou2-bu2 hou7 thong se3-kai3 e5 lang5 , long2-chong2 chai-iaN2 un7-tong7 e5 iau3-kin2, long2-chong2 tui3 un7-tong7 u7 chhu3-bi7; lang5-lang5 long2 khi3 cho3. Tui3 an2-ni, thong se3-kai3 e5 lang5 sin-the2 kap cheng-sin5 chiu7 chiam7-chiam7 e7 khah iong2-chong3. 
