  Ah! Se-iuN5-lang5 pi2 lan2 khah iong2 u7 pah-poe7, pi2 lan2 khah gau5 u7 chheng-poe7; sit8-chai7 m7-si7 ngou2-jian5 e5 tai7-chi3. Goan7 lan2 tui3 un7-tong7 tioh8 koh chit8-hoan e5 iong7-sim. Sit8-chai7 ¡§Bo5 hioh-khun3 long2 cho3-kang, khiau2-khiau2 gin2-na2 to tioh8 piN3 gong7-lang5.¡¨ ChhiaN2 put-si5 cho3-kang e5 tong5-pau tioh8 ai3 e7 ki3-tit. Koh-chai3 Lo5-ma2-lang5 u7 kong2 , ¡§Kian7-khong ti7 mng5-goa7 .¡¨ Sou2-i2 goa2 ho2-taN2 chhiaN2 ui7-tioh8 put-si5 kan-ta an-cheng7 hioh-khun3 , ti3-kau3 phoa3-peN7 teh kan-khou2 e5 tong5-pau , chhiaN2 lin2 sin3 Lo5-ma2-lang5 chit ku3 oe7, si5-si5 chhut-khi3 mng5-khau2-goa7 kiaN5-kiaN5 chau2-chau2 khoaN3, kian7-khong iong2-kiaN7 tek-khak ti7-hia tan2-hau7 lin2! 
