  I-chiuN5 , chiah8-mih8 kap chu7-ki, chit saN-hang7 si7 lang5 beh po2-chhi5 seN3-mia7 sou2 pit-iau3--e5. Chong2-si7 lang5 ui7-tioh8 chit saN-hang7 tian-to3 sun2-sit seN3-mia7--e5 ia7-si7 u7. M7-na7 si7 u7 na7-tiaN7; chiau3 sit8-chai7 khoaN3, lan2 e5 lang5 ui7-tioh8 tui3 chit saN hang7 ¡§I, Sit8 , Chu7 , ¡¨ an-pai5 liau2 u7 m7 tu2-ho2, chhek-te2 sou2 eng-kai hiong2-siu7 e5 hoe3-siu7 si7 chin-che7. 
  (1) I-chiuN5 e5 lou7-eng7 , te7-it si7 beh tiau-chiat koaN5-joah8, kau7-poh8 chheng7 e7 tu2-ho2, si7 hui-siong5 iau3-kin2. Che7-che7 lang5 kong2 saN-a2-khou3 chheng7 poh8 khah ai3 kam2-tioh8 hong, chheng7 kau7 chiu7 khah be7. Bo5 tek-khak tu2-tu2 si7 an2-ni. Khiok m7-si7 kong2 kau7-poh8 long2 bo5 koan-he7; chong2-si7 choe3 u7 koan-he7 si7 chai7 the2-chit e5 kiong5-jiok8, put-chai7 saN-a2-khou3 e5 hun7-liong7. Lang5 e5 kam2-kak e7 hun3-lian7-tit, e7 koan3-si3, siong5-siong5 chheng7 kau7 e5 lang5 kau3-boe2 soa3 koan3-si3, phoe5-hu tui3 an2-ni chiu7 pian3-chiaN5 be7 kham-tit leng2, sio2-khoa2 koaN5 to tioh8 chheng7 chin kau7. 
  M7-ku2 na7-si7 tui3 khi2-thau5 chiu7 chu3-i3 chheng7 khah poh8 , kau3 boe2 koan3-si3, sui-jian5 si7 chin koaN5, ia7 si7 m7-bian2 chheng7 siuN kau7. Goa2 e5 chhin-lang5 , peng5-iu2 e5 tiong-kan, cho3 i-seng e5 lang5 put-chi2 nng7 saN lang5, goa2 siong5-siong5 khi3 in e5 sou2-chai7, khoaN3-kiN3 chin-che7 toa7-lang5 pho7 i e5 gin2-na2 beh hou7 sian-siN khoaN3. Hian7-hian7 si7 lak8-goeh8 thiN chin joah8, ia7 ka7 i e5 gin2-na2 chheng7 kui2-na7 nia2 saN koh thah8 hiu5, thau5-khak ka7 i ti3 bo7-am. Sian-siN beh ka7 i chin2-chhat, chit8-e7 ka7 i thng3-saN khoaN3, kho2-lin5 hit e5 gin2-na2 hou7 m7-bat cheng5-li2 e5 toa7-lang5 , ka7 i hip kau3 chit8 seng-khu choan-choan koaN7, chhau3-koaN7-sng e5 hian3 chha-put-to beh kek-to2 lang5. 
  Lang5 u7 nng7-cheng2 e5 chhoan2-khui3, chit8 cheng2 si7 tui3 phiN7-khang kap chhui3 , koh chit8 cheng2 si7 tui3 mng5-kng2-khang. Chhin-chhiuN7 chiah joah8 e5 si5, ka7 gin2-na2 pau kau3 hit khoan2, che kiat-kiok8 si7 chiong hiah e5 mng5-kng2-khang long2 ka7 i that-bat8, m7 hou7 i chhoan2-khui3, gin2-na2 m7-bian2 kam2-tioh8 hong, i2-keng tioh8 ai3 phoa3-peN7 chiah u7 hap8 cheng5-li2. I-chiuN7 e5 lou7-iong7, bian2 kong2 chit8-pou7 si7 beh po2-chhi5 tui3 lang5 e5 le2-sou3, ia7 chit8-pou7 si7 beh ho2-khoaN3 chng-sui2; chong2-si7 choe3 toa7 e5 lou7-iong7 si7 beh pang-chan7 phoe5-hu tiau-chiat thiN-khi3 e5 koaN5-joah8. ChhiaN2 tioh8 koh e7 ki3-tit chit8-hang7:khi3-hau7 leng2 e5 si5 chu7-jian5 tioh8 ai3 chheng7 khah kau7; chong2-si7 na7 tui3 peng5-si5 chu3-i3, e7 thang chheng7 ju2-poh8 si7 ju2-ho2, hou7 seng-khu e7 ju2-iong2. Gin2-na2 joah8-thiN teh khun3 e5 si5, kan-ta ka7 i pau pak-tou2 , kha-chhiu2 heng-kham2 hou7 i liang5 si7 bo5 iau3-kin2. 
  E5 thang kong2 ia7 si7 chit8 cheng2 e5 saN-a2-khou3. Lan2 e5 hiaN-ti7 kha thng3 chhiah-chhiah e5 lang5 chin-chiaN3 che7, chit8 hang7 si7 chin thang kian3-siau3, chin thang hoan5-lo2. An2-ni m7-na7 si7 ia2-chong7 phaiN2-khoaN3, ui7-tioh8 an2-ni kha-kut seN liap8-a2 kan-khou2 e5 lang5 si7 chin-che7. Kin7-lai5 hiong-chhoan e5 chi2-moe7 liu5-kha liau2, che si7 toa7-toa7 thang hoaN-hi2; chong2-si7 soa3 oh8 ta-pou-lang5 thng3 chhiah-kha, chit hang7 chin-chiaN3 ai3 chhiaN2 tai7-ke siuN7! TaN m7-chai beh an2-choaN2 lai5 kai2-kiu3? 
  (2)Chiah8 mih8 e5 tai7-chi3, lan2 ai3 koan-sim e5 tiam2 u7 chin-che7. Lan2 e5 lang5 put-lun7 chiah8 a2-si7 lim, long2 tioh8 koe3 chu2, koe3 hiaN5 , koe3 kun2 chiah kheng2 chiah8, chit hang7 si7 chin ho2 e5 hoat-tou7. In-ui7 mih8-nih siong5-siong5 u7 tiau5 chin iu3-se3 e5 thang5 kio3-cho3 se3-khun2, lang5 e5 phoa3-peN7 tui3 chiap-tioh8 chit hang7 lai5--e5 si7 chin-che7. Na7 chit8 pai2 ka7 i koe3 chu2 koe3-khi3, i chiu7 sui5-si5 si2--khi3, chiah8-liau2 chiu7 bo5 iau3-kin2. 
  Chong2-si7 lan2 tui3 chit hang7 chiah8, choe3 m7-ho2 e5 sip8-koan3 chiu7-si7 ai3 loan7-loan7 chiah8, long2 bo5 chiau3 si5-chun7. Chiau3 i-seng e5 gian2-kiu3 kong2, lang5 tui3 chhui3-lai7 chiah8 mih8 jip8 pak, tioh8 keng-koe3 ji7-chap8-saN tiam2-cheng chiah e7 pang3 chhut-lai5. Chiah8-mih8 thun loh8-khi3 ui7 e5 lai7-te2 (ui7, phou2-thong kio3-cho3 tou7 ) tioh8 keng-koe3 chit8 tiam2-cheng chiah choan2 jip8 khi3 sio2-tng5, tioh8 chhit tiam2-cheng ku2 hiah e5 mih8 chiah e7 thong-koe3 sio2-tng5 e5 sou2-chai7. Thong-koe3 sio2-tng5 i2-au7 choan2 jip8-khi3 toa7-tng5 lai7; ti7-hia u7 chap8-gou7 tiam2-cheng ku2, jian5-au7 chiah e7 siau chhut-lai5 goa7-bin7. 
  Ti7 teng2-chat u7 kong2, Cho3-kang kap hioh-khun3 tioh8 ai3 chun2-chat e7 tu2-ho2; ti7-chia chit hang7 ia7 si7 iau3-kin2. Chiah8-mih8 jip8-khi3 pak-tou2-lai7, pak-lai7 e5 ki-koan chiu7-si7 ui7, sio2-tng5, toa7-tng5, i2-goa7, koaN, io-chi2, ui7-tioh8 beh hou7 hiah e5 chiah8-mih8 e7 thang siau cho3 seng-khu e5 lou7-eng7, long2 tioh8 ai3 cho3 kang; na7-si7 bo5 hioh-khun3 , kau3 chit8 si5 lat8 chhut chin7, iah8 chiu7 to2-loh8--khi3, iah8 chiu7 hoat phoa3-peN7. Se-iuN5 u7 chit8 ku3 siok8-gu2 kong2, ¡§Tng5 chhai3 e7 cho3 te2 seN3-mia7.¡¨ Lan2 ia7 u7 chit8 ku3 kong2, ¡§TiuN3 ti pui5, tiuN3 kau2 san2, tiuN3 lang5 ng5-sng-than2.¡¨ Bo5 mih8 thang chiah8 go7-si2 e5 lang5 sit8-chai7 si7 chin-che7; chong2-si7 hou7 mih8 tiuN3-si2 e5 lang5 tak8 jit8 m7-chai u7 loa7-che7? Koh-chai3 cho3 chit8 pai2 chiah8 siuN che7 tiuN3-si2--e5 e7 thang kong2 si7 bo5, sou2 u7 hou7 mih8 tiuN3-si2--e5 long2 si7 tui3 ti7 bo5 siu2 si5-kan, chhui3 put-si5 tang7, chit8 chhui3 chiah8 koe3 chit8 chhui3--e5 khah che7. Iau-kui2 chiu7-si7 go7-kui2 e5 chhiok-ho7, chhiaN2 u7 thang chiah8 e5 lang5 tioh8 sio2-sim! 
  Chhui3 put-si5 tang7 e5 lang5, m7-na7 e7 chhek-te2 hoe3-siu7, iau2-ku2 hou7 thau5-nau2 hun7-tun7 be7 hiau2 siuN7 tai7-chi3. Tai7-ke ka-ti7 chhi3-giam7 khoaN3 , tai7-khai3 pak khin, sim chiu7 khin, pak-tou2 na7 pa2 bak8-chiu chiu7 beh ai3-khun3. Sou2-i2 khah bo5 chhou-tang7 siong5-siong5 iong7 thau5-nau2 e5 lang5, kin7-lai5 hiam5 chit8 jit8 chiah8 saN-tng3 siuN koe3 che7, sou2-i2 chit8 jit8 chhek chiah8 nng7 tng3 e5 u7 chin-che7. U7 lang5 chhek cha2-khi2 tng3 bo5 chiah8, u7 lang5 chhek e7-tau3 tng3. Chit khoan2 lang5 goa2 chai-e5 put-chi2 che7. 
  Goa2 ka-ti7 chu7-gou7. Lak8 ni5 cheng5 ti7 Tang-kiaN e5 si5 khi2, chiu7 kan-ta chiah8 tiong-tau3 tng3 kap am3-tng3, cha2-khi2 tng3 si7 chha-put-to bo5 chiah8, kan-ta lim chiaN5 oaN2 am2-moe5 chiu7 soah. Goa2 keng-giam7 liau2 kam2-kak put-chi2 ho2. Sou2-i2 chhiaN2 ui7-tioh8 san3-hiong e5 ian5-kou3 chiah8 nng7 tng3 e5 liat8-ui7 m7-bian2 siong-sim, u7 thang chiah8 e5 lang5 ia7 teh oh8 lin2 e5 ho2 bou5-iuN7. Chiah8-mih8 u7-si5 chit8 poaN3-pai2 chiah8 hou7 i chin chiok pa2, hou7 pak-tou2 lai7 khah lau7-jiat8 ia7-si7 ho2; chong2-si7 peng5-sou3-si5 chiah8 kau3 peh-hun kau2-hun iau2 khah ho2. Na7-si7 an2-ni m7 han7-tiaN7 pak-tou2 khah khoaN3 oah8, sou2-chiah8--e5 loh8 khi3 liau2 e5 mih8 e5 ho2 bi7, iah8 beh ku2-ku2 te7-teh phang. 
  Koan-he7 chiah8-mih8 tioh8 koh siuN7 chit8 hang7: chiah8-mih8 jip8 chhui3-lai7 tioh8 jin7-chin pou7 hou7 iu3, loh8 khi3 pak-tou2 chiah khoai3-siau. Tui3 an2-ni chiu7 thang chai-iaN2 chhui3-khi2 si7 chin tioh8 chiau3-kou3. Lan2 e5 lang5 e5 chhui3-khi2 chin khoai3 chiu3, khoai3 lak. Che long2 si7 tui3 be7-hiau2 chiau3-kou3 sou2 ti3--e5. Chiau3 khoaN3 m7-bat se2-chhui3 e5 lang5 si7 chin che7. Chhui3, na7 bo5 tak8 jit8 se2, sou2 chiah8 e5 mih8 e7 tiau5 ti7 khi2-hoaN7, chhui3-khi2 tui3 an2-ni chiu7 khoai3 lak. M7-na7 an2-ni; chhui3-lai7 e5 bi7 sit8-chai7 si7 bo5 ho2, chhui3 na7 thi2-khui ia7-si7 bo5 nga2-khi3. 
  Kin7-lai5 tai7-ke chiam7-chiam7 u7 beng5-pek8 chit8-hang7, tak8 cha2-khi2 se2-bin7 e5 si5 soa3 se2 chhui3. Se2 chhui3 e5 si5 tai7-khai3 si7 iong7 khi2-bin2 kap khi2-hun2. Khi2-bin2 si7 tek-khak ai3; khi2-hun2 si7 m7-bian2 tek-khak, kan-ta iong7 khah iu3 e5 iam5 chiu7 chiok-giah8. Iam5 , u7 khi3 tok8-khi3 e5 lat8. Koh-chai3 tak8 tng3 chiah8-pa2 au7 tioh8 ai3 iong7 chui2 soa2-khau2, chiong tiau5 ti7 chhui3-khi2 hiah e5 mih8 se2 hou7 i li7, chiah ho2. Chit hang7 tek-khak tioh8 sit8-heng5, beh hou7 chhui3-khi2 iong2, chit hang7 si7 chin u7 kong-hau7. Beh khun3 e5 si5 na7-si7 u7 koh soa2 chit pai2 chhui3, si7 iau2 khah teng2-chin. Na7-si7 kong2 lau7-lang5 u7 chhui3-khi2 si7 e7 pou7-si2 kiaN2-sun, che si7 chit cheng2 e5 be5-sin3, si7 chin put-kin7 jin5-cheng5 e5 oe7. 
  Lan2 e5 chiah8-mih8 e5 chu2-hoat kap chai7 hian7-si5 choan5 se3-kai3 pat8-lang5 pheng7, sit8-chai7 si7 be7 su--lang5. Chong2-si7 goa2 khoaN3 ho2-chiah8, si7 ho2-chiah8, m7-chai e7 khah bo5 oe7-seng a2-be7? Goa2 siuN7, kiaN-liau2 e7 khah oh siau-hoa3, in-ui7 lan2 iong7 iu5 siuN koe3 che7, koh-chai3 mih8 siong5-siong5 chu2-liau2 siuN koe3-thau5, ti3-kau3 oh-tit siau. Chhin-chhiuN7 lou2-nng7 khiok si7 chin ho2-chiah8; m7-ku2 si7 chin be7 siau. Lan2 chiong5-lai5 chiah8-png7, iah8 si7 chin m7-tioh8 hoat-tou7, lan2 long2-si7 chiah8 hou5--e5, kan-ta theh8 hiah e5 bi2-phoh khi2-lai5 chiah8, bi2-chhoe2 long2 ti7 am2-lai7, chiong hiah e5 chu-iong2 e5 am2-chiah theh8 khi3 chhi7 ti, chiuN-saN; sit8-chai7 si7 chin m7-tioh8. Iah8 lan2 Tai5-oan5 koe2-chi2 chhut chin che7, tai7-ke m7-chai si7 ui7-tioh8 sim2-mih8 in-toaN, long2 chin han2-tit chiah8; che iah8-si7 chin kho2-sioh. Koe2-chi2 m7-na7 u7 ham5 chin-che7 e5 chu-iong2-hun ti7-teh, chiah8 liau2 ia7 put-chi2 e7 pang-chan7 pat8-hang7 mih8 siau-hoa3. 
  Chu7-ki e7 thang kong2 ia7 si7 chit8 cheng2 e5 saN-a2-khou3, si7 kui ka-chok8 e5 lang5 kong-ke ti7-teh chheng7--e5. Sou2-i2 ti7 teng2-cham7 lun7 i chiuN7 e5 sou2-chai7 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7, ti7-chia e7 iong7-tit koh kong2. I-chiuN5 si7 beh cho3 chun2-chat koaN5-joah8 e5 lou7-eng7 , chu7-ki ia7 si7 an2-ni. I-chiuN5 si7 beh chan7 lang5 e5 bi2-koan, hou7 lang5 ho2-khoaN3; chu7-ki ia7-si7 u7 chit8 hang7 e5 lou7-eng7. Koh-chai3 i-chiuN5 si7 lang5 tui3 lang5 e5 le2-sou3 lai5 kong2, tek-khak tioh8 ai3 e5 mih8, chu7-ki ma7-si7 tang5 chit8-iuN7. I-chiuN5 si7 kan-ta u7 chit saN-khoan2 e5 lou7-eng7; chong2-si7 chu7-ki m7-na7 si7 an2-ni, ia7 beh hong5-pi7 chhat8-a2 e5 thau-theh8. Lan2 e5 chhu3 che7-che7 ai3 khi2 hiong3 sai, che sit8-chai7 si7 siuN pek-joah8, put-chi2 m7-ho2. Put-ko3 ia7 tioh8 khoaN3 sou2-chai7, khiok be7 iong7-tit it-khai3 lun7. 
  M7-ku2 na7-si7 chiau3 chiong5-lai5 thok te7-li2-su an lo5-keN chiah teng7 hong-hiong3, hit khoan2 si7 chin chho3-gou7. Beh khi2-chhu3 e5 si5 te7-it iau3-kin2 tioh8 keng2 ta-sang e5 sou2-chai7, tioh8 khoaN3 si3-ui5 e5 sou2-chai7 chiah teng7 hong-hiong3, ai3 hou7 jit8 chio3 e7 tioh8, hong thong e7 kau3, sou2-i2 thang-a2 tioh8 khui khah che7 khah toa7--e5. Chhu3 e5 chiu-ui5 na7-si7 u7 te7-tiuN5 thang chai chhiu7-bak8 hoe-chhau2 si7 chin ho2, in-ui7 chhiu7-bak8 e5 hioh8 e7 se2 chheng lang5 tui3 phiN7-khang teh suh e5 khong-khi3. 
  Chhu3-lai7 e5 mih8-kiaN7 na7-si7 e7 ju2 chio2 ju2 ho2. Lan2 e5 chhu3-lai7 siong5-siong5 u7 bo5 lou7-eng7 e5 mih8 tin3 kau3 moa2-moa2, sit8-chai7 si7 chin tin3-te3, chin bo5 ho2-khoaN3. Sou2-hui3 kiaN-liau2 siuN tang7 cho3 be7 kau3; na7 beh m7-si7 chhu3-lai7 long2-chong2 phou te7-pan2, tak8 jit8 iong7 chui2 jiu5 se2 hou7 i chheng-khi3, ti7 goa7-bin7 sou2 chheng7 e5 hia, e5, bak8-kiah8 long2 mai3-tit chheng7 khi2-lai5 teng2-bin7, an2-ni chhu3-lai7 chiu7 e7 chin chheng-khi3 , toa7-se3 tek-khak e7 khah chio2 peN7-thiaN3. Chiong chit pou7 ui7-tioh8 peN7-thiaN3 e5 ioh8-chiN5, kap kiam2 cho3 kang e5 sun2-sit, phah-sng3 chiu7 i2-keng chiok-giah8, oe7-thang cho3 cheng2-tun3 chhu3-lai7 e5 hui3-iong7. Koh chit8 hang7: chhu3-teng2 e5 kak-a2 boh8-tit phou khui-khui, hou7 thou5-soa e7 thang seh loh8-lai5, na7 long2 eng7 pang phou hou7 bat8 chiu7 chin hap8 li2-siong2, chhin-chhiuN7 Loe7-te7-lang5 kap Goa7-kok-lang5 e5 chhu3, koa3 hit khoan2 thian-pong5; na7-si7 tui3 lan2 e5 chhu3 e5 khi2-hoat kong2, goa2 siuN7 si7 bo5 pit-iau3. 
  Lan2 u7 ai3 tiam3 chhu3-lai7 chhi7 cheng-seN e5 sip8-koan3. Hian7-si5 ke-chhi7 khiok khah bo5, chai7 chng-sia7 si7 chin che7 lang5 u7 chhi7. Lun7 chhi7 cheng-seN si7 chit8 hang7 toa7 su7-giap8, si7 chin iau3-kin2; chong2-si7 tioh8 m7-thang ai3 beh hou7 cheng-seN pui5, ti3-kau3 hou7 lang5 san2 chiah e7 iong7-tit. Na7-si7 ti7 chhu3 e5 tiaN5-thau5 tiaN5-boe2, leng7-goa7 siat chit8 sou2-chai7 chhi7 si7 chin ho2, m7-ku2 chiau3 sou2 khoaN3-kiN3 , si7 pang3 kap lang5 teh lam7 e5 khah toa7 pou7-hun7. In-ui7 an2-ni tiaN5-nih e5 thou5-kha to bian2-kong2, chiu7-si7 thiaN5-nih lai7-bin7 ia7 si7 put-si5 u7 ke, ah, a2-si7 ti, iuN5 ti7-teh lam7, cham2-jian5 bo5 chheng-khi3. 
  Iah8 chng-sia7 lai7 e5 lou7-nih, chit-tah hit-tah khah che7 long2 si7 u7 m7-ho2 e5 bi7 thang kek-to2 lang5. Hit ho7 m7-ho2 e5 bi7 , chiu7-si7 u7 tok8-khi3 e5 cheng3-ku3, he put-chi2 e7 hai7 lang5 e5 seng-khu, e7 hou7 lang5 khoai3 phoa3-peN7. Lan2 to bo5 ka7 i chhi3-giam7 khoaN3, chai7 hit sou2-chai7 in-ui7 chhi7 cheng-seN sou2 than3 e5 chiN5-gin5, m7-chai u7 kau3 thiah ioh8 a2-bo5? 
  Goa2 na7 jip8-khi3 chng-sia7 e5 si5, tiaN7-tiaN7 to si7 siuN7 kong2 , chng-goa7 e5 chhan5-iuN5 na7 phi3-lun7 cho3 kek8-lok8 e5 Thian-kok, chng-lai7 chiu7-si7 kan-khou2 e5 Te7-gek8. In-ui7 chhan5-iuN5 kui phian3 long2 si7 chheN-leng-leng, chhan5-thau5 chhan5-boe2 u7 oah8-thiau3-thiau3 e5 chui2 teh lau5; tui3 ti7 chhan5-bin7 chhoe--lai5 e5 hong iu7 liang5, iu7 phang, tiu7-a2-boe2 hou7 hong chhoe tam3--leh, giah8--leh; chit8 chong7 chhin-chhiuN7 lek8 e5 chui2 teh ek. 
  Bo5 tiuN-ti5, tui3 bin7-cheng5 e5 chhau2-a2-lai7, u7 lan2 sou2 be7 hiau2-tit e5 thang5-thoa7 chhoe-chhiuN3 geng5-chiap lan2; theng5-cheng7 , chit8-e7 thiaN--khoaN3, m7-chai ti7 to2 chit8 kek, tui3 koan5-koan5 e5 sou2-chai7 u7 poaN3-thiN-a2 e5 siaN se3-se3 ti7-teh hiang2. Theng5-kha kiah8-thau5 chit8-e7 khoaN3, hng7-hng7 e5 soaN tit8-tit8 kau3 beh tu2-thiN; chai7-chai7 kah-na2 chhin-chhiuN7 ti7-teh khun3. Ah! Sui2 ah! chu7-chai7 ah! khoai3-lok8 ah! lan2 e5 chhan5-iuN5 e5 ho2 keng2-ti3! 
  M7-ku2 na7 jip8-kau3 lan2 e5 chng-sia7 lai5, thau5 chiu7 ai3 hin5, bak8 chiu7 ai3 hoe. Sou2 u7 khoaN3-kiN3--e5 , chiu7-si7 tek-chhi3 e5 phoa3 li5-pa, ju5 kaN3-kaN3 e5 chhau2-tui, ti teh ko7-ek8 e5 chhau3-chui2-khut, thou5-pun3-tui, chiuN3-lok8-lok8 e5 ti-tiau5. Ke, kau2 e5 siaN loan7-chhau-chhau, hu7-jin5-lang5 hau2-hoah e5 siaN hou7 lang5 chhang3 mng5-kng2. Bak8-chiu sou2 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 long2 si7 hong-hoe3, hi7-khang sou2 u7 thiaN-kiN3 , to si7 lo5-cho5; toa7-lang5 chheN-gin7-gin7 , kan-ta ui7-tioh8 saN-tng3 chiah8, thoa-boa5 m7-kaN2 sio2-khoa2 theng5, gin2-na2 bo5 lang5 thang koan2-kou3, kap ke, kau2 siang7 ti7 thou5-kha teh pe5 teh hau2. Ah! Chit khoan2 e5 keng2-hong2 , beh ka7 phi3-ju7 cho3 sim2-mih8? Sui-si7 te7-gek8 , ia7 kaN2 ma7 si7 chit e5 iuN7! 
  Tai7-ke chiong3-ui7 tong5-pau! Put-heng7 teng2-bin7 sou2 kong2--e5, na7 ko2-jian5 si7 lan2 e5 chng-sia7 lang5 teh koe3-jit8 e5 hian7-chong7, lan2 pang3 hou7 i chiau3 chit e5 se3-bin7 khi3 e7 iong7-tit be7? Toan3-toan3 be7 iong7-tit! Lan2 tek-khak tioh8 siuN7 chit8 hang7 kai2-kiu3 e5 hoat-tou7. Chiau3 goa2 e5 gu5-gian5 , chit khoan2 phaiN2 keng2-gu7 e5 goan5-in , te7-it, si7 chai7 lan2 ku2 ni5 kau3-iok8 bo5 phou2-kip8; te7-ji7, choan5-jian5 si7 tui3 pin5-san3 e5 ian5-kou3. PhaiN2 sip8-koan3 kap bo5 kau3-iok8 , che tioh8 ban7-ban7 lai5 kai2-kek, pin5-san3 si7 khah khoai3 thang kai2-kiu3. 
  Lan2 e5 chng-sia7 lang5 si7 chin khin5-bian2, koh-chai3 tui3 ka-ti7 chit8 sin e5 hui3-iong7, iah8 si7 chin khiam7-phok. An2-ni si7 bo5 pun5-san3 e5 li2-iu5. M7-ku2 chiau3 sit8-chai7, toa7 pou7-hun7 si7 chin keng5. Che si7 in-ui7 chau2-lau7 e5 sou2-chai7 hui-siong5 che7. Chau2-lau7 e5 lou7 lin2 ka-ti7 chhiaN2 siuN7-khoaN3. Ti7-chia goa2 sou2 m7-ai3 kong2--e5 u7 chin-che7, goa2 kan-ta kong2 kui2-tiau5 khah phou2-thong khah khoai3 kai2-kiu3 e5 tiam2. 
  Thau5 chit8 hang7: keng3 pai3 sin5-beng5 e5 hoat-tou7 u7 toa7 m7-tioh8. Kok lang5 sou2 sin3 e5 sin5-beng5 tek-khak tioh8 ai3 keng3-pai3 chiah eng-kai, che put-lun7 to2-loh8 e5 lang5 to si7 chit8-iuN7; lan2 ia7 tioh8 an2-ni cho3. M7-ku2 keng3-pai3 e5 hong-hoat, lan2 si7 toa7-toa7 kap lang5 bo5 sio-siang7. Lan2 e5 lang5 ui7-tioh8 sin5-beng5 khai bo5 i3-su3 e5 chiN5 si7 bo5 tang3 thang khi3 sng3. Lan2 sou2 keng3 e5 sin5 m7-na7 chit8 sian , si7 pah-pah sian; sou2-i2 kim-jit8 u7 sim2-mih8 seN, bin5-jit8 tioh8 che3 sim2-mih8 sin5. Chit-goeh8 Ma2-chou2 beh koah-hiuN, au7-goeh8 Ong5-ia5 beh chhut-sun5. Khah-theng5 kong2 beh phou2-tou7 , bo5 chit8 tiap-a2-ku2 iu7 tioh8 ai3 cho3 chio3. Koh-chai3 chit8-ni5 kan sou2 ai3 cho3 e5 ki7-sin5 m7-chai kui2-pai2; sng3, to sng3 put-chin7. Na7 lun7-kau3 khi2 bio7-u2 chng kim-sin, teng2-teng2 sou2-hui3 e5 chiN5, kheng5-chin kaN2 e7 kiaN--lang5. 
  Hian7-kim kan-ta chai7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 kong2, chiong-kin7 u7 nng7-chheng lang5 mui2 jit8 phah-piaN3 cho3 kim-choa2 bo5 hu3 hou7 lang5 sio. Tai7-ke ui7-tioh8 sin5-beng5 e5 tai7-chi3 kan-ta loan7 sio, loan7 nau7, loan7 lim, loan7 chiah8 e5 sou2-hui3, chit8 ni5 kok lang5 kok khau2-chau3 tioh8 ai3 loa7 che7 chiah u7 kau3? Pat8 sou2-chai7 e5 lang5 chhin-chhiuN7 lan2 pai3 sin5-put8--e5 si7 u7, pai3 chiong2-chiong2 e5 chho2-bok8-sin5 ia7 si7 u7, chong2-si7 bo5 chit8 tah u7 lan2 chit khoan2 e5 khai-hui3. Chit khoan2 e5 khai-hui3 kiam2 m7-si7 e7 seng2-iok-tit mah? Kan-ta saN ni5 ku2, chiong sou2 seng2-iok e5 chiN5 kia3 tiam3 gin5-hang5 khng3, chhiaN2 sng3 khoaN3 chit8 khau2-chau3 m7-chai7 beh chek loa7-che7 neh? 
  Ui7-tioh8 koan3, hun, song, che3, lan2 pheng7 pat8-kok e5 lang5 ke khai e5 chiN5 ia7 si7 hui-siong5. Lun7 ke3-chhoa7 e5 tai7-chi3, lau2-sit8 si7 cho3 lang5 it-seng e5 toa7-su7. Iah8 song-su7 che3-su7 che khiok ia7-si7 jin5-cheng5 e5 le2-sou3, si7 cho3 kiaN2-sun e5 lang5 sou2 m7-kaN2 lo2-chho2 e5 pun2-hun7. M7-ku2 na7 chiau3 hian7-si5 e5 hong-siok8 khoaN3, sit8-chai7 long2 si7 siu2 heng5-sek khah che7, long2 bo5 u7 sim2-mih8 sit8-sim. Goan5-lai5 lang5 e5 kian3-bun5 ju2 tiong2, sim-khiau3 chiu7 ju2 khui, chit ho7 jin5-cheng5 hong-siok8, tek-khak tioh8 kap si5-tai7 peN5-peN5 kai2-oaN7 chin3-pou7 chiah si7. 
  Chai7-cha2 lan2 e5 cheng5-tai7 e5 gau5 lang5 , kiam2 m7-si7 u7 ka3 lan2 tioh8 put-si5 cho3 sin-siuN3 e5 lang5 mah? Chong2-si7 kho2-sioh lan2 tong5-pau e5 tiong-kan , iau2-ku2 be7 thang hiau2-ngou7 chu7-sin, chiah8 ou-hun, lim sio-chiu2, chhoa7 se3-i5, cheng2-cheng2 e5 phaiN2 sip8-koan3, thoat long2 be7 thang li7 e5 lang5 si7 chin-che7. Kan-ta chiau3 teng2-bin7 sou2 kong2, ui7-tioh8 ngia5-sin5, keng3-put8, koan3, hun, song, che3 , sou2 ke khai-hui3 e5 chiN5-giah8 chek-thiok khi2-lai5, chiong chiah e5 chiu7 beh u7 thang hou7 lan2 e5 kiaN2-ji5 thak8-chheh siu-iong2, hou7 lan2 e5 chhu3-lai7 khah u7 cheng2-li2, toa7-se3 khah be7 peN7-thiaN3, khah e7 thang hoaN-hi2 koe3-jit8. Lan2 chit e5 Tai5-oan5 si7 se3-kai3 tiong han2-tit u7 chit8 e5 thian-jian5 e5 po2-khou3, lan2 hian7-hian7 tiam3 ti7 chit e5 po2-khou3-lai7, tioh8 kau3 chit khoan2 e5 pin5-san3 kan-khou2, che sit8-chai7 si7 chin-chiaN3 put-hap8 li2. 
  C. Chheng-kiat. 
  Tui3 chit-ku3 ¡§Chheng-kiat¡¨, phah-sng3 tai7-ke tek-khak leng7-goa7 u7 chit8 cheng2 koh-iuN7 khoan2 e5 kam2-kak. ThiaN-tioh8 ¡§Chheng-kiat¡¨ kiam2 m7-si7 sui5-si5 siuN7-tioh8 keng2-chhat kap chit8 cheng2 kiaN-hiaN5 e5 sim. Chit saN e5 liam7-thau5 chai7 lan2 e5 thau5-nau2-lai7, kah-na2 chhin-chhiuN7 put-si5 saN-chhoa7-kiaN5 e5 khoan2. Lau2-sit8 chiu7 leng2 Tai5 i2-lai5 , chai7 lan2 tai7-ke Pun2-to2 lang5 e5 tiong-kan, ui7-tioh8 keng2-chhat e5 giam5-tok, siu7-tioh8 koe3-thau5 khek-khui--e5 si7 be7 chio2; chong2-si7 na7 tui3 tai7-kiok8 khoaN3, ui7-tioh8 an2-ni, chheng-kiat e5 tai7-chi3 u7 ke chin toa7 chin3-pou7. Na7 chiong keng2-chhat sou2 u7 cho3 koe3-thau5 e5 tai7-chi3, mai3-tit khioh lai5 kong2, sit8-chai7 chit chan5 e5 chin3-pou7, thang kong2 si7 Pun2-to2 keng2-chhat-kai3 e5 kong-lo5. M7-ku2 na7 koh tui3 chit8-bin7 siuN7-khoaN3, chiu7 thang beng5-pek8 lan2 e5 tong5-pau chiong5-lai5 si7 khah bo5 chheng-kiat, lan2 tioh8 tui3 sim-koaN te2 ka-ti7 chap8-hun chu7-jin7 chu7-chek, toa7 kian3-siau3 chiah tioh8. 
  Chheng-kiat u7 nng7-khoan2 e5 i3-gi7: Chit8 khoan2 chiu7-si7 sun5-sui3 bo5 hun7-chap8, tan-tan chit8 hang7 e5 i3-su3. Phi3-lun7 chia u7 thng5: lan2 na7 kong2 chiah e5 thng5 u7 chheng-kiat, u7 chheng-khi3 bo5, chiu7-si7 teh mng7 kong2 khoaN3 hiah e5 thng5 si7 kan-ta thng5 na7-tiaN7, a2-si7 u7 chham pat8-mih8 khoan2 e5 mih8 ti7-teh. Na7-si7 bo5 pat8-mih8 chham-teh, chiu7-si7 chheng-khi3; na7-si7 u7 pat8 khoan2 mih8 chham-teh, put-lun7 si7 chham iam5 a2-si7 hun2, a2-si7 thou5-soa-liap8, put-koan2 si7 e7 chiah8-tit, a2-si7 be7 chiah8-tit ; hiah e5 thng5 chiu7-si7 bo5 chheng-khi3, chiu7-si7 la5-sam5. 
  Koh phi3-lun7 chit8 hang7: na7 kong2 chit8 nia2 saN se2-liau2 u7 chheng-khi3, chiu7-si7 kong2 chit nia2 saN--nih bo5 pat8 hang7 mih8 tiau5-teh, si7 kan-ta pou3-se na7-tiaN7; na7-si7 kong2 la5-sam5 , chiu7-si7 pou3-se i2-goa7 iau2 u7 pat8-hang7 mih8 tiau5-teh, u7 thou5 a2-si7 u7 koaN7, u7 iu5-ko3 tiau5-teh e5 i3-su3. 
  Chheng-kiat iau2 u7 chit8 khoan2 e5 i3-gi7. Te7-ji7 e5 i3-gi7 si7 bo5 tok8; bo5 tok8 chiu7-si7 chheng-kiat. U7 chit8 jit8 goa2 tui3 Tai5-tiong che7 chhia beh tng2-lai5 Tai5-lam5. U7 chit8 e5 saN-chap8 cho2-iu7 hoe3 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 , sin-piN he7 chit8 e5 pau-hok8, che7 ti7 goa2 e5 tui3-bin7. I e5 gin2-na2 chha-put-to u7 si3-hoe3 , kha-nih chheng7 chit8 siang pou3-e5, khia7 ti7 i2-teng2 teh kiaN5, sou2-i2 i2-teng2 in3 kau3 choan-choan thou5-soa e5 e5-te2-jiah. Goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 i long2 bo5 liah8 he cho3 an2-choaN2; jim2 be7 tiau5, khui-chhui3 ka7 i kong2, ¡§Li2 e5 i2-teng2 i2-keng chin la5-sam5 , gin2-na2 e5 e5 chhiaN2 ka7 i thng3--khi2-lai5, chaiN2-iuN7?¡¨ Hu7-jin5-lang5 thiaN-kiN3 goa2 an2-ni kong2, i chiu7 kin2-kin2 chiong i e5 chhiu2 chhit hiah e5 thou5-soa, iah8 chiah chiong i e5 chhiu2-kin chhit i e5 chhiu2, au7-lai5 i koh thng3 gin2-na2 e5 e5, chiong hit siang e5-a2 e5-te2 hip e5-te2, thau2-khui pau-hok8 cho3-hoe2 pau loh8-khi3. Goa2 ka7 i khoaN3, pau-hok8 lai7 u7 pau chiah8-mih8 ti7-teh. 
  Ah! Goa2 khoaN3-liau2 tian-to3 siuN7 chin m7 koe3-sim: in-ui7 goa2 kong2 chit8-ku3 ai3 i chheng-khi3, hoan2-tng2 hou7 i cho3-chhut chin-che7 bo5 chheng-khi3 e5 tai7-chi3. Ban7-it hit siang e5 na7 u7 tiau2-tok8 ti7-teh, pau-hok8-lai7 hiah e5 chiah8-mih8, chiah8-liau2 na7 khi2 phoa3-peN7, iah8 m7 chin hai7! KhoaN3 hit e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 khiok si7 bo5 sim2-mih8 u7 tiok8-lok8; chong2-si7 chai7 lan2 tong5-pau e5 lai7-te2 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 chit khoan2 lang5, goa2 sit8-chai7 chit8-si5 khah chham2 hou7 lang5 kong3 saN e7 thau5-khak-oaN2. Che si7 in-ui7 i kan-ta e7-hiau2 u7 chhap-chap8 e5 la5-sam5, be7-hiau2 u7 tok8 e5 la5-sam5. I si7 siuN7 kong2, thou5-soa to i2-keng chhit khi2-lai5 liau2, chhiu2-kin au7-lai5 se2 chiu7 e7 chheng-khi3, iah8 e5 to te2 hip te2, thou5-soa be7 bak-tioh8 chiah8-mih8, sou2-i2 i chiah liah8-cho3 bo5 iau3-kin2. Phah-sng3 i kaN2 si7 siuN7 an2-ni. Che si7 tui3 i be7-hiau2 u7 tok8 sou2 ti3--e5. 
  Loe7-te7-lang5 put-chi2 ai3 chheng-khi3; tui3 in chit e5 seng3-chit goa2 put-chi2 toa7 kam2-sim. Chong2-si7 goa2 khi3 Loe7-te7 chhit-ni5 goa7 ku2, goa2 iah8 si7 bat khoaN3-kiN3 in e5 lang5 u7 bo5 chheng-khi3 e5 sou2-chai7. Loe7-te7-lang5 put-chi2 ai3 se2-ek8, sou2-i2 kau3 to2-ui7 to u7 ek8-keng chin chiaN3 che7. Goa2 iah8 si7 nng7 jit8 saN jit8 khi3 ek8-keng se2 chit8 pai2. Chin chhu3-bi7, ek8-keng si7 beh hou7 lang5 chheng-khi3 e5 sou2-chai7, m7-ku2 goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 Loe7-te7-lang5 tiong u7 be7-hiau2 chheng-khi3 e5 lang5, si7 ti7-chia khoaN3-kiN3. Khiok m7-si7 kong2 tak8 e5 Loe7-te7-lang5 long2 an2-ni; chong2-si7 goa2 tiaN7-tiaN7 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 khah chhou-siok8 e5 Loe7-te7-lang5 , loh8-khi3 ek8-thang2-lai7 se2 e5 si5, siong5-siong5 u7 lang5 iong7 ek8-thang2 chui2 kam5 khi2-lai5 se2 chhui3, iah8 chhui3-lai7 hiah e5 chui2 phui3 tiam3 thang2-goa7 e5 lang5 iah8 si7 u7; chiu7 an2-ni phui3 tiam3 thang2-lai7--e5 iah8 si7 u7. U7 tang-si5-a2 iah8 bat khoaN3-kiN3 pho7 gin2-na2 loh8-khi3 se2, chiong bin7-pou3 un3 ek8-thang2 chui2 ka7 gin2-na2 se2-chhui3--e5 ia7 si7 u7. Hit ho7 ek8-keng e5 ek8-chui2, si7 pah-pah cheng2 e5 lang5 se2-liau2--e5, keng3-jian5 iah8 ui7-tioh8 beh hou7 chhui3 chheng-khi3, chiong hit ho7 chui2 lai5 se2, khi2 m7-si7 beh chheng-khi3 , tian-to3 lah-sap mah? 
  Chhin-chhiuN7 chit khoan2 lang5 khiok m7-si7 kong2 chin-che7; m7-ku2 khah che7 e5 Loe7-te7-lang5 na7 loh8-khi3 ek8-thang2 lai7. Chiu7 hou3 chui2 khi2-lai5 se2 thau5 se2 bin7, che si7 chha-put-to lang5-lang5 u7 an2-ni. Tui3 an2-ni goa2 chiu7 siuN7 kong2 Loe7-te7-lang5 e5 ai3 chheng-khi3 , iah8 iau2-ku2 si7 chhian2-chhian2. In-ui7 tui3 chit hang7 u7 tok8 e5 la5-sam5, in iah8 iau2-ku2 si7 bat bo5 kau3. 
  Na7 kong2 lan2 e5 lang5 to si7 iau2 khah hai7, lan2 e5 hiaN-ti7 chi2-moe7 e5 tiong-kan , u7 tok8 e5 la5-sam5 to bian2 kong2, chiu7-si7 chhap-chap8 e5 la5-sam5 be7-hiau2 e5 lang5 si7 hui-siong5 che7. Tiong-kok-lang5 si7 kap lan2 siang7 chou2-kong, sou2-i2 tui3 chit hang7 bo5 chheng-kiat e5 tai7-chi3 si7 kap lan2 saN-siang7 khoan2. In-ui7 an2-ni Tiong-kok-lang5 chai7 kin-a2-jit8 e5 se3-kai3 siu7 lang5 khoaN3 khin chin-che7, iah8 lan2 iah8 si7 siang7 chit8 iuN7. 
  U7 tok8 e5 la5-sam5 kap chhap-chap8 e5 la5-sam5 , lan2 e5 lang5 nng7 hang7 long2 bat bo5 chin, eng3-kai lan2 e5 lang5 chha-put-to tioh8 long2 cheh8-cheng2 chiah tioh8. Ho2 kai-chai3, lan2 long2 bo5 chiah8 chheN-mih8 , long2 tioh8 koe3-chu2 koe3-hiaN5 chiah u7 chiah8 u7 lim; tui3 an2-ni u7 tok8 e5 e5 la5-sam5 siau bo5-khi3 chin-che7, sou2-i2 chiah e7 thang khah-chio2 si2-sit. Kong2 khah-chio2 si2-sit si7 tui3 cheng5-li2 siuN7 teh kong2; na7 lun7 pi2 pat8 tah lang5 si7 ke si2 hui-siong5 che7. Lan2 e5 lang5 ui7-tioh8 be7-hiau2 la5-sam5, pheng7 lang5 si7 chin te2 hoe3-siu7. Si2-lang5 chhiaN2 boh8-tit kong2, in-ui7 la5-sam5 ti3-kau3 pai2-kha, chheN-me5, bo5 chhui3-khi2, chit khoan2 lang5 chai7 lan2 tiong-kan si7 se3-kai3 it-teng2 che7. Ai5--ah! Chit khoan2 chaiN2-iuN7 tui3 lang5 u7 nga2-khi3 neh? 
  Goa2 khoaN3 lan2 khah bo5 chheng-khi3-siuN3 e5 goan5-in u7 saN-e5:
  Thau5-chit8-e5 si7 tui3 lan2 bo5 hak8-bun7, m7-bat oe7-seng. 
