  Te7-saN-e5 si7 in-ui7 chui2 m7-ho2 koh chio2. 
  Lang5 bo5 hak8-bun7 , put-lun7 tui3 sim2-mih8 to si7 m7-ho2; chong2-si7 tui3 oe7-seng e5 tai7-chi3 na7-bo5 hak8-bun7, si7 tit8-chiap chek-si5 u7 m7-ho2 thang khoaN3-kiN3. Lan2 in-ui7 bo5 hak8-bun7, sou2-i2 sim2-mih8 si7 chheng-khi3 , sim2-mih8 si7 la5-sam5, lan2 bat be7 chin7. U7 tok8 si7 sim2-mih8 i3-su3 lan2 be7 hiau2-tit, ti3-kau3 tioh8 liau2 seN3-mia7, tioh8 phoa3-siuN3, kan-khou2. Tok8 e5 lai7-te2, phi3-lun7 chhin-chhiuN7 se3-khun2 hit chit8 chiong2, he si7 oah8 e5 mih8, si7 chin se3-boe2 e5 thang5 , si7 lang5 bak8-chiu sou2 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3--e5, iah8 si7 chin-chiaN3 gau5 seN-thoaN3. ThiaN-kiN3 kong2, chhin-chhiuN7 lau3-thou3-cheng3, a2-si7 niau2-chhu2-cheng3, chit khoan2 e5 tok8-thang5 , chit8-jit8 kan-ta chit8-boe2 e7 thang pian3-cho3 chheng-chheng ban7-ban7 boe2, sou2-i2 lang5 na7 hou7 chit khoan2 thang5 chhim-hoan7-tioh8; m7-bian2 chit8-jit8 goa7 chiu7 si2. 
  Eng2-pai2 khah-cha2, chai7 goa2 chhut-si3 e5 hiuN-li2 (Pak-kang2), bat chit8-si5 niau2-chhu2-cheng3 chin toa7 liu5-heng5, u7 chit8 ke-khau2 gou7-e5 lang5 cho3 chit8 le2-pai3 ku2 si2 kau3 chhun chit8 lang5. Che si7 in-ui7 bo5 ti3-sek; be7-hiau2 chit khoan2 tok8-thang5 e5 li7-hai7, be7-hiau2 hong5-pi7 , tou3-lai5 tou3-khi3 chiah e7 an2-ni. In-ui7 lan2 bo5 hak8-bun7, ui7-tioh8 chit khoan2 niau2-chhu2-cheng3, chit khoan2 tok8-thang5 , oan-ong2 si2 e5 lang5 m7-chai u7 loa7-che7? 
  Lang5 na7 bo5 hak8-bun7 , m7-na7 chheng-kiat e5 hoat-tou7 be7-hiau2 , tioh8 ai3 siu7 khek-khui, koh-chai3 bo5 hak8-bun7 e5 lang5 keng-che3 tek-khak m7-ho2, sui-jian5 si7 e7-hiau2 beh chheng-khi3, in-ui7 bo5 chiN5, khui3-lat8 cho3 be7 kau3-e5, iah8 si7 hui-siong5 che7. Tui3 chit tiam2 kong2, goa2 iah8 toa7-toa7 hi-bong7 lan2 tong5-pau cheng3-lang5, tioh8 ai3 khoaN3 hak8-bun7 khah-tang7 leh. Hak8-bun7 si7 lang5 beh koe3 chit8-si3-lang5 e5 tou7-chun5. Lan2 e5 chi2-moe7 chha-put-to si7 long2-chong2 bo5 thak8-chheh, tui3 chit chan5 goa2 sit8-chai7 si7 hui-siong5 thong3-sim chhim-chhim teh hoan5-lo2! 
  Lan2 e7 khah bo5 chheng-kiat , te7-ji7 e5 goan5-in, goa2 kong2 si7 in-ui7 hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 lan2-to7. Lan2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 chiau3 phou2-thong khoaN3 si7 chin thoa-boa5, put-si5 kan-ta cho3-kang long2 bo5 hioh-khun3. Na7 an2-ni, chaiN2-iuN7 goa2 kong2 lan2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 lan2-to7? Goa2 m7-si7 kong2 lan2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 ban7-hang7 long2 lan2-to7; goa2 si7 kan-ta kong2 lan2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 tui3 chit hang7 chheng-kiat e5 tai7-chi3, si7 put-chi2 lan2-to; si7 kan-ta tui3 chheng-kiat e5 tai7-chi3 ti7-teh kong2. Chheng-kiat e5 tai7-chi3, tai7-khai3 long2 si7 khah ai3 chhou-tang7, iah8 lan2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 long2 si7 u7 pak8-kha, sou2-i2 kiaN5-chau2 khah be7 chu7-iu5, be7 thang peh-koan5 loh8-ke7, in-ui7 bo5 un7-tong7 kan-ta che7 teh ut, ti3-kau3 sin-the2 lam2, kin-kut bo5 lat8 thang tin2-tang7. Tui3 an2-ni piaN3-sau3 chiu7 khah lo2-chho2, ju2 la5-sam5 chiu7 ju2 koan3-si3, iah8 koan3-si3 chiu7 soa3 pian3 chu7-jian5. Bou2 la5-sam5 , ang iah8 chiu7 bo5 hoat-tou7, tioh8 soa3 lah-sap chham loh8-khi3, iah8 sou2 seN--chhut lai5 e5 gin2-na2 to bian2 kong2. Kau3-boe2 soa3 hoat-beng5 chit8 cheng2 la5-sam5 e5 chin-li2. La5-sam5 e5 lang5 kong2, ¡§Chiah8 thou5 khah toa7 bou5¡¨; ¡§Chiah8 thang5 gau5 cho3-lang5 ;¡¨ ¡§Ou-sek e5 saN-a2-khou3 khah be7 la5-sam5;¡¨ ¡§Se2-ek8 ai3 kam2-tioh8 hong-sia5;¡¨ ¡§Thng3 chhiah-kha choa5 m7-kaN2 ka7¡¨ (kong2 in-ui7 Siong7-te3 kong si7 chhiah-kha). Che long2 si7 lan2 e5 La5-sam5-lang5 tek8-piat8 che3-cho7 e5 chin-li2, si7 pat8 tah sou2 bo5-e5! Kin7-lai5 hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 pak8-kha si7 chiam7-chiam7 liu5 beh liau2, sin-the2 iah8 chiam7-chiam7 khah iong2, khah chu7-iu5; chong2-si7 chit khoan2 thong thiN-kha-e7 sou2 bo5-e5 la5-sam5 chin-li2, m7-chai ti7-si5 chiah e7 siau-biat8 khi3? 
  Te7-saN e5 goan5-in, goa2 kong2 si7 in-ui7 chui2 chio2. Chit tiau5 khiok m7-si7 kin-pun2 e5 goan5-in, si7 pang-chan7 lan2 la5-sam5 chit8-e5 tit8-chiap e5 tong7-ki na7-tiaN7. Chai7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 chiong5-lai5 beh tit ho2 e5 chui2 si7 chin kan-ke3 . Tai7-khai3 khe-chui2 long2 si7 bo5 sim2-mih8 chheng, cheN2-chui2 e5 chit, iu7 si7 bo5 thang ho2-e5 khah che7. Chit8 peng5 bo5 thian-jian5 e5 ho2-chui2, koh chit8 peng5 lan2 iu7 bo5 ti3-sek, bo5 kang2-kiu3 beh hou7 chui2 ho2 e5 hoat-tou7. In-ui7 chui2 phaiN2, hou7 lang5 seN-chhut be7-hiau2 la5-sam5 si7 sim2-mih8--e5, si7 chin-che7. Chui2 e5 chheng, lo5, sit8-chai7 si7 toa7-toa7 u7 koan-he7 lang5 e5 chheng-khi3 kap lah-sap. Loe7-te7 lang5 khah ai3 chheng-khi3-siuN3. Goa2 khoaN3 Loe7-te7 tak8 tah e5 khe-chui2 , cheN2-chui2 to si7 chin chheng , siu7 che e5 kam2-hoa3 to si7 be7 chio2. 
  Iu7 koh-chai3 lan2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 long2 khah be7 chhou-tang7, sou2-i2 beh taN-chui2 chhiuN7-chui2 chiu7 khah oh-tit, pou7-pou7 tioh8 ta-pou-lang5 , a2-si7 tioh8 chhiaN3 lang5 taN. Tui3 an2-ni , chu7-jian5 chiu7 khah ai3 po2-sioh chui2, ai3 chin khiam7-iong7. Siok8-gu2 soa3 u7 chit ho7 oe7 kong2, ¡¨Gau5 iong7 chui2 e5 lang5, au7-chhut-si3 tioh8 cho3 niau.¡¨ cheng3-lang5 tui3 chui2 e5 koan-liam7 si7 chit khoan2, sou2-i2 lan2 e5 lang5 han2-tit se2 seng-khu; u7-si5 kan-ta chhit na7-tiaN7, bin7-thang2-chui2 pi2 kau-a2-chui2 khah lo5, iah8 m7-si7 han2-han2-tit. 
  Ah! Goa2 kong2 kau3 chia iah8 m7-kam koh-chai3 kong2, iah8 goa2 iah8 si7 bo5 iong2-khi3 thang koh kong2. ThiaN-kiN3 koan2 chui2-to7 e5 lang5 kong2, chit8 e5 lang5 chit8 jit8 na7 si7 iong7 gou7-tau2 poaN3 e5 chui2 si7 eng-kai. TaN lan2 chit8 jit8 m7-chai iong7 joa7-che7? Chheng-kiat si7 kap sin-the2 e5 iong2-lam2 choe3 thau5 it-teng2 u7 koan-he7. Ban7-hang7 e5 chheng-kiat si7 tui3 tak8-lang5 e5 thau5-nau2 seng-khu cho3 khi2-thau5. Beh hou7 thau5-nau2 chheng-kiat, chiu7 tioh8 u7 hak8-bun7, u7 kau3-iok8; beh hou7 sin-the2 chheng-kiat, chiu7 tioh8 se2 seng-khu. 
  Ai3 lan2 hiaN-ti7 chi2-moe7 u7 kau3-iok8 , ho2 e5 hak8-hak8 koaN2-kin2 siat khah che7, si7 chin chhiat-iau3; chong2-si7 beh kiu3 hian7-si5 e5 kin2-kip, goa2 kong2 tioh8 chi3-kip phou2-kip8 Lo5-ma2-ji7. Na7 m7-si7 phou2-kip8 Lo5-ma2-ji7, hian7-si5 chai7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 , cheng3-lang5 tui3 kau3-iok8 e5 khoeh-khiam3 , sit8-chai7 bo5 lou7 thang pou2-chiok. Iah8 na7 beh hou7 cheng3-lang5 e7 thang khah chheng-kiat , tek-khak tioh8 e7 thang hou7 tai7-ke kok lang5 seng-khu khah chheng-khi3. 
